OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Ffading leaving a generally dry night.
OL,7,FLight winds and clear skies will allow
OL,8,Fa little shallow mist and fog to form
OL,9,Fin prone areas. Feeling fresher for
OL,10,Fsome, but a warm and humid night to
OL,11,Fcome in the south.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FA fine and dry day ahead with
OL,14,Flots of sunshine though a small risk
OL,15,Fof the odd light shower. Feeling warm,
OL,16,Fthough a hot, humid day ahead in the
OL,17,Fsouth.
